{
  "chunk_id": 1,
  "start_offset": 1190.0,
  "segments": [
    {
      "idx": 0,
      "start": 1190.0,
      "end": 1196.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我如果只是一個想掙投機的想掙錢的人我會做，但是如果我是一個真正",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 1,
      "start": 1196.0,
      "end": 1201.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "知識分子，我不願意那樣做，我寧願自己多花點錢去買書。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 2,
      "start": 1201.0,
      "end": 1206.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果我們都去賣盜版的話，那以後誰還會花心思去研究？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 3,
      "start": 1206.0,
      "end": 1208.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "沒有人研究還有誰去著書立作？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "start": 1208.0,
      "end": 1213.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "抄襲是最容易的方式，但抄襲是從根本上傷害了創新的最直接的方式。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "start": 1215.0,
      "end": 1220.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "晚清最後18年這套書講的是從袁世凱，袁世凱從朝鮮回來之後發生的事情。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 6,
      "start": 1220.0,
      "end": 1229.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "這本書非常打動我的就是在北洋水師甲午海戰的時候，當時強盛的帝國從來沒有想到自己在一個彈丸小國面前輸的如此顏面盡失。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 7,
      "start": 1229.0,
      "end": 1231.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "其實並不是因為他不過強大。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 8,
      "start": 1231.0,
      "end": 1238.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "後人在總結歷史的時候,總事看不清全貌,覺得是我們太弱小了,如果當時用來買更多的艦艇會不會好一些？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 9,
      "start": 1238.0,
      "end": 1240.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我相信這本書能給你一個清晰的答案。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 10,
      "start": 1240.0,
      "end": 1244.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就是已經到了戰場上，各方勢力仍然在角逐。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 11,
      "start": 1244.0,
      "end": 1250.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "已經到了關鍵的要分勝負的時候，大家心裡仍然沒有堅定決心去作戰。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 12,
      "start": 1250.0,
      "end": 1255.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "大家想的是多年經營的李中堂,如此強大的北洋水師,這麼多艦艇都是白花花的銀子。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 13,
      "start": 1255.0,
      "end": 1256.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我不能輸。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 14,
      "start": 1256.0,
      "end": 1258.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "一旦輸了打沉了,錢白花了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 15,
      "start": 1258.0,
      "end": 1260.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "第二個我也不會贏。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 16,
      "start": 1260.0,
      "end": 1264.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "因為贏了之後,沒有了外部威脅之後,北洋水師是否還有存在的必要性？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 17,
      "start": 1264.0,
      "end": 1266.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "一群軍人不考慮軍人的問題。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 18,
      "start": 1267.0,
      "end": 1269.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "一群大臣不考慮大臣的問題。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 19,
      "start": 1269.0,
      "end": 1272.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "這就是那個時代的悲哀,所以那個時代注定的悲哀,",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 20,
      "start": 1272.0,
      "end": 1276.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就是因為在其崗位卻不考慮他崗位的職責。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 21,
      "start": 1276.0,
      "end": 1279.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以我當時讀完這本書之後,就告訴了孩子們一段話。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 22,
      "start": 1279.0,
      "end": 1285.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "好多年前在西安新東方的課堂上,我給孩子們說,正確的初衷才是最強大的力量。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 23,
      "start": 1285.0,
      "end": 1291.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "請你記住,它勝過一切高超的智慧和任何細膩的手法。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 24,
      "start": 1293.0,
      "end": 1297.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "只有最強大的力量才能支撐你走到最後。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 25,
      "start": 1298.0,
      "end": 1302.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那些心懷不軌的人,那些不忠誠於使命的人,",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 26,
      "start": 1302.0,
      "end": 1307.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那些從一開始就沒有正確出心的人,他可能會靠著自己的小聰明蒙騙一時,",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 27,
      "start": 1307.0,
      "end": 1309.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但大多數會在黎明前倒下。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 28,
      "start": 1310.0,
      "end": 1313.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就算有那麼一兩個幸運的,好像多走了幾步,",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 29,
      "start": 1314.0,
      "end": 1315.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那他會更尷尬。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 30,
      "start": 1316.0,
      "end": 1321.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "因為他會在太陽正頭頂的時候,於眾目睽睽之下倒在你面前。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 31,
      "start": 1322.0,
      "end": 1324.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他不僅輸,他還輸的會更加徹底。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 32,
      "start": 1324.0,
      "end": 1331.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以這套書在當年我特別年輕的時候,我覺得他也從很大一個程度上糾正了我的價值觀。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 33,
      "start": 1331.0,
      "end": 1334.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "或者說加強了我的價值觀,最後影響了我的價值觀。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 34,
      "start": 1334.0,
      "end": 1337.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "正確的初衷才是最強大的力量。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 35,
      "start": 1338.0,
      "end": 1340.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "永遠不要忘記你為什麼出發。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 36,
      "start": 1340.0,
      "end": 1344.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "當一個人開始背棄自己理想的時候,他不會成功的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 37,
      "start": 1344.0,
      "end": 1346.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他再聰明都不會成功的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 38,
      "start": 1346.0,
      "end": 1347.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他擁有",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 39,
      "start": 1348.0,
      "end": 1349.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "困難。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 40,
      "start": 1350.0,
      "end": 1351.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但請你三觀不改。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 41,
      "start": 1352.0,
      "end": 1356.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "這就是為什麼我向屏幕前的每個朋友推薦晚清最後18年。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 42,
      "start": 1357.0,
      "end": 1358.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "它應該有兩本書。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 43,
      "start": 1358.0,
      "end": 1360.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "是吧？這好像是個改編版,我當時讀的一共會有四本。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 44,
      "start": 1360.0,
      "end": 1361.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "這是",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 45,
      "start": 1361.0,
      "end": 1362.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "精華版是吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 46,
      "start": 1362.0,
      "end": 1365.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那可能就故事更加的集中一些,也挺好,也挺好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 47,
      "start": 1365.0,
      "end": 1367.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "讀一些精華版,大家可能時間也更加快一些。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 48,
      "start": 1367.0,
      "end": 1369.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "除了這個還有那本呢,是這個嗎？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 49,
      "start": 1370.0,
      "end": 1372.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "對,這是兩本書啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 50,
      "start": 1373.0,
      "end": 1376.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "晚清最後18年,推薦給屏幕前的每一個朋友。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 51,
      "start": 1377.0,
      "end": 1380.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我剛所說的這個正確的初衷,其實就是你為什麼而出發。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 52,
      "start": 1380.0,
      "end": 1382.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "在商業世界裡頭就是你要解決什麼問題？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 53,
      "start": 1383.0,
      "end": 1386.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "在具體崗位上就是你要創造什麼價值？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 54,
      "start": 1386.0,
      "end": 1388.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "在家庭裡頭就是你為什麼在奮鬥？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 55,
      "start": 1390.0,
      "end": 1394.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "每一個環節裡都可以去問一問自己,什麼才是你真正正確的初衷？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 56,
      "start": 1395.0,
      "end": 1396.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "這個很重要。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 57,
      "start": 1396.0,
      "end": 1398.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就是",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 58,
      "start": 1399.0,
      "end": 1401.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "what do you fight for,你在捍衛什麼？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 59,
      "start": 1403.0,
      "end": 1404.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你在捍衛什麼？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 60,
      "start": 1404.0,
      "end": 1406.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "your mission,",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 61,
      "start": 1406.0,
      "end": 1408.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你的使命感是什麼？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 62,
      "start": 1408.0,
      "end": 1409.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "your goal,",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 63,
      "start": 1410.0,
      "end": 1411.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你的目標是什麼？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 64,
      "start": 1411.0,
      "end": 1412.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "這些很重要。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 65,
      "start": 1412.0,
      "end": 1418.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "只有正確的使命,正確的目標才會給你足夠多的內驅力,drive,足夠多的內驅力。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 66,
      "start": 1418.0,
      "end": 1421.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "足夠多的內驅力才會讓你走得很遠,而且走得很穩妥。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 67,
      "start": 1422.0,
      "end": 1426.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "大家見過很多聰明人,依靠自己的聰明,一招取勝的故事,很多對吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 68,
      "start": 1426.0,
      "end": 1430.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "太多這種投機取巧的故事,會讓一個時代變得輕浮。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 69,
      "start": 1433.0,
      "end": 1436.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "羅翔有句話說這個",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 70,
      "start": 1437.0,
      "end": 1439.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "來得晚的正義算不算正義？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 71,
      "start": 1439.0,
      "end": 1440.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "有很多人討論過這個問題。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 72,
      "start": 1441.0,
      "end": 1442.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "算正義。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 73,
      "start": 1442.0,
      "end": 1443.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "只要來了就行。",
